Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Project Sekai After Talk: Beyond the Untangled Threads Edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Izumi Rina, the voice of Hinomori Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from MORE MORE JUMP! It's a pleasure to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This After Talk is a broadcast where we look back at the event story
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and enjoy the After Live together. This is the 'Beyond the Untangled Threads' edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The event just finished a moment ago. How did you all like the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so much I want to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So many things happened, and I want to talk about them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please post your thoughts on the event using the hashtag #ProsekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff has set up the YouTube chat so I can see it right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be reading your comments as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The management provided a device again, so I'll use it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at the story and the illustrations of the members with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For today's After Live, I'll be operating the device myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to join a room and watch the live show with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll create a room ID right before the After Live starts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can all enter it at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You might need to switch devices or apps, so I'd appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could get everything ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's look back at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're reviewing the story for 'Beyond the Untangled Threads'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see comments like, "The entertainment industry is so scary,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt that the way Shizuku faced her past
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,was so cool when I first read the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The story really depicts the realistic behind-the-scenes side of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There were some quite painful scenes, but because Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,faced them head-on without running away, she was able
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach that kind of conclusion to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to tell Shizuku she did a great job,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and say thank you to the members of MORE MORE JUMP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk more in-depth about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to watch one episode with everyone here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which episode would you like to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the intense battle during the filming of I-Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 7 or 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding the story of her past...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen fragments of her time in Cheerful＊Days before,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time it really delved deep into what specifically happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to choose, but maybe 7 or 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there are a lot of votes for 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go with 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is 7 okay with everyone?
Comment: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, let's watch Episode 7 together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching it with all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,makes it so much more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.00,0:27:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.40,0:27:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see people in the YouTube chat saying it's emotional and sending applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.00,0:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.80,0:28:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to head out soon to prepare for the next part.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.12,0:28:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll keep my thoughts brief for now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.60,0:28:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Shizuku's past like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.80,0:28:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku is such a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.36,0:28:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She has such a strong will. This scene really highlighted her strength in being able to say "thank you" face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it into words, and to have the courage to do it right in the middle of filming...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.10,0:28:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku is the coolest person in the world for being able to clearly express everything she wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.02,0:28:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just want to give her a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.08,0:29:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In my heart, I'm already hugging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.54,0:29:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.68,0:29:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shizuku doesn't get angry, but Airi-chan gets all fired up for her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.88,0:29:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That dynamic is just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.52,0:29:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It captures that intense idol atmosphere, and Airi-chan's part in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.04,0:29:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some thoughts on that too, so I'd like to talk about it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.36,0:29:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.00,0:48:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.38,0:48:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice being able to watch this with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.56,0:48:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.08,0:48:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is just racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.19,0:48:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.32,0:48:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.18,0:48:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a new song this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.10,0:48:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the new song we briefly introduced during the last WonderShow Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.32,0:48:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.24,0:49:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-chan has sung many different songs up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.62,0:49:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt like we were able to see different sides and expressions of her each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.48,0:49:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was a different kind of coolness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.92,0:49:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that we got to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.00,0:49:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this was an After Live, seeing it as a performance with the costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.52,0:49:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything came together and looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.48,0:49:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The way it went dark for a moment before the pre-chorus, and then Len-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.60,0:49:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,came to the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.44,0:49:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really loved the lighting in that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.06,0:49:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was truly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.60,0:49:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The high notes were wonderful, and the recording session was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.40,0:49:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When it came to the recording this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.12,0:49:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Comment: 0,0:49:53.84,0:49:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.84,0:49:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just the theme,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.16,0:49:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.84,0:50:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in this scenario, Shizuku took that first step and went even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.24,0:50:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.60,0:50:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing Shizuku get her wings and awaken... I felt this song has that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.40,0:50:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I received the materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.52,0:50:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the lyrics were filled with so many emotions, so
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.60,0:50:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to express them with everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.88,0:50:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What we just showed you was the game-size version.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.96,0:50:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we'll have the chance to share the full version with you somewhere, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.56,0:50:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.04,0:50:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love for you to feel Shizuku's sense of taking flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.46,0:50:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,especially after the second chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.64,0:50:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to hear the full version!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.20,0:51:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But even in this version,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.92,0:51:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of the chorus,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.84,0:51:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the feeling of "having nothing left to fear" really reached everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.60,0:51:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was absolutely wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.86,0:51:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then everyone waves their hands, and the stage suddenly brightens up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.00,0:51:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that part
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.96,0:51:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.52,0:51:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.04,0:51:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much for getting excited with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.12,0:51:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This 3DMV was posted on the official Proseka YouTube channel today at 10:10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.32,0:51:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already started,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.52,0:51:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's already up, so please go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.76,0:51:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.84,0:51:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd appreciate your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.64,0:51:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.60,0:52:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like for us to take a look at the newly added illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.04,0:52:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are five of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.60,0:52:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cards are all so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.04,0:52:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start by looking at Shizuku's.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.59,0:52:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.80,0:52:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.44,0:52:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the "After Training" version.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.36,0:52:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.92,0:52:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The large flower Shizuku is sitting on...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.92,0:52:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it has this stained glass feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.48,0:52:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a glass-like texture that I really love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.04,0:52:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a certain fleeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.64,0:52:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,fragile beauty to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.04,0:52:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can really feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.98,0:52:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the "Before Training" version.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.84,0:53:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this illustration was shown first.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.92,0:53:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit of Arisa was visible in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.64,0:53:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the image posted on Twitter and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.15,0:53:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.68,0:53:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.04,0:53:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is this woman?"
Comment: 0,0:53:20.56,0:53:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.56,0:53:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This illustration too...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.48,0:53:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at this one alone, Shizuku has such a cheerful expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.16,0:53:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Airi is going "shaa," and Arisa has this "huff" look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.88,0:53:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really funny once you've seen the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.60,0:53:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.96,0:53:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.48,0:53:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love this. Arisa is great, and Airi's expression is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.10,0:53:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.80,0:53:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.52,0:53:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.60,0:53:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.28,0:53:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.06,0:54:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total change from Shizuku's outfit, with black and white and red accents...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.48,0:54:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.84,0:54:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.40,0:54:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she's wearing a leaf on her head...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.48,0:54:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...is just so cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.16,0:54:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I called her a Korpokkur earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.64,0:54:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because she has this really fairy-like vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.96,0:54:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the Pre-Trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.74,0:54:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Snacking time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.00,0:54:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.16,0:54:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like the ProSeka recording sites. In the waiting room...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.84,0:54:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...they always provide us with delicious food. Everyone really...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.84,0:54:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We got bento today too. Having snacks laid out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.12,0:54:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...is actually quite realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.16,0:54:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nervous before the show, but the snacks are so good you eat them anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.36,0:54:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.60,0:54:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should definitely check out the side story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.38,0:55:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.04,0:55:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.68,0:55:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.64,0:55:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And next is Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.68,0:55:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is her Trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.32,0:55:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The outfit is similar to the one Minori was wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.10,0:55:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the skirt is slightly different. Airi has flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.36,0:55:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...spread out like a pannier. It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.24,0:55:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.80,0:55:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The droplets scattered around her make it feel like the rain just stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.52,0:55:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that kind of feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.92,0:55:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...really reminds me of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.44,0:55:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the Pre-Trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.04,0:55:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This scene was in the story too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.00,0:55:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi is always...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.12,0:55:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...worrying about Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.42,0:55:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll say, "Hey, you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.28,0:55:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.72,0:55:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku tends not to speak up about things,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.80,0:56:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so Airi is always looking out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.32,0:56:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is.
Comment: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.96,0:56:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Airi, the Shizuku we know today wouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.60,0:56:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even back in her Cheerful Days era, Airi...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.99,0:56:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.68,0:56:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...encouraged her so much during her Cutie Days. You can really see their bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.44,0:56:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.04,0:56:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Training art is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.32,0:56:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.52,0:56:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...the frog looks so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.84,0:56:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this expression just so cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.24,0:56:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's landing on a leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.00,0:56:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.78,0:56:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's outfit isn't just red, it has some orange in it too, which is...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.60,0:56:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...so incredibly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.04,0:56:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These subtle differences in the outfits are...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.80,0:56:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.74,0:56:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hatsune Miku looks incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.68,0:56:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.99,0:57:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.76,0:57:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the pre-Training version.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.52,0:57:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the actual filming studio for AiHaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.96,0:57:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The background, the camera crew, the exit sign in the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.88,0:57:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...the way the emergency lights look...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.84,0:57:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the monitor in the bottom right under the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.60,0:57:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It really looks exactly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.36,0:57:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The perspective you have when standing in a studio with cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.84,0:57:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka here...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.84,0:57:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...looks so nervous, like she's right about to go on for the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.60,0:57:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This expression is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.88,0:57:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.50,0:57:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.80,0:57:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're constantly filming different expressions from various angles...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.08,0:57:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...switching between cameras to create the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.36,0:57:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...that everyone usually sees. So this is what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.96,0:57:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.00,0:58:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.16,0:58:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Meiko, you look so elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.84,0:58:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This white... this white outfit is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.94,0:58:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it suits her so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.08,0:58:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.76,0:58:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.16,0:58:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.82,0:58:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding the flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.72,0:58:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...she's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.64,0:58:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the sleeves flare out a bit is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.04,0:58:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.96,0:58:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at this, I wanted to write that the group name got smaller...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.40,0:58:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...but because of the character limit, it just says "got small."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That happens sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.40,0:58:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 0,0:58:48.08,0:58:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.08,0:58:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The outfit is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.96,0:58:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually quite simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.64,0:58:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.00,0:59:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone pointed it out to me, but looking at Shizuku's outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.88,0:59:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.38,0:59:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw the illustration, I just thought she looked like a fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.20,0:59:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just giggling at how cute she was, but then someone told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.18,0:59:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that this might be based on Thumbelina. Now, for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.40,0:59:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I obviously knew the title "Thumbelina,"
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.64,0:59:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd never actually read the story properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.04,0:59:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I looked up what kind of story it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.12,0:59:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's about a tiny girl born from a flower who gets named Thumbelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.88,0:59:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets kidnapped and faces all sorts of dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.88,0:59:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She really goes through a lot of difficult things.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.60,0:59:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the very end, a swa... swallow?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.90,0:59:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A swallow saves her,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.84,0:59:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and she finds freedom in a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.39,0:59:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.76,0:59:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are these swallows?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.64,1:00:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The black and white...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.68,1:00:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Minori-chan,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.48,1:00:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi-chan, and Haruka-chan. Now that you mention it, they do look like swallows.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.60,1:00:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The yellow on their chests looks like a beak. Whoever noticed that is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.82,1:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.92,1:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes so much sense now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.84,1:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes how I see it. There's even a frog here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.44,1:00:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A frog appears in Thumbelina too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.40,1:00:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It all clicks for me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.72,1:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.12,1:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of Thumbelina is about how if you don't give up,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.44,1:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your dreams come true and you can be free.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.80,1:00:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "That's exactly this story!" Shizuku is saved by the swallows,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.56,1:00:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and now she can spread her wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.08,1:00:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so emotional, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.96,1:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it feels. Thank you for the info.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.92,1:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.20,1:01:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at the end of "The Untied Thread,"
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.04,1:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the story and everything come together, and the illustration is just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.04,1:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.04,1:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.60,1:01:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I really want to talk about Arisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.12,1:01:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In this story,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.92,1:01:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it's structured, Shizuku and the Cheerful＊Days members clash quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.04,1:01:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from a certain perspective, Arisa-chan and the other former Cheerful＊Days girls
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.94,1:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,might seem like the villains. There were many moments where you'd think, "Oh, these girls..."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.00,1:01:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.44,1:01:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei-chan said it too. They're all serious about being idols, and they all seriously wanted
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.84,1:01:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that center position Shizuku had. They're girls who have worked incredibly hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.54,1:02:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they get so genuinely jealous and put in so much effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.80,1:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Comment: 0,1:02:07.80,1:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.80,1:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite intense.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.48,1:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Arisa was such a straightforward girl...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.72,1:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.36,1:02:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.48,1:02:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment Arisa and the others met
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.68,1:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the members of Tiade...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.64,1:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Arisa was like, "I'm going all out,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.80,1:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'd better do the same."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.56,1:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She really puts those feelings into words for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.84,1:02:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.16,1:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought her straightforwardness, always giving it her all,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.88,1:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,was...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.92,1:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,really cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.50,1:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.36,1:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.76,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hiding things like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.84,1:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she went about it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.52,1:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't the best way to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.63,1:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.68,1:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.92,1:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.84,1:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad thing to have those feelings because you want to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.08,1:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that those "damn it" feelings come from being serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.84,1:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to learn from that. I felt like it wasn't just someone else's problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.72,1:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you direct those feelings of jealousy the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.32,1:03:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,really bad things can happen. It's difficult to handle those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.28,1:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to find a way to deal with them inside yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.44,1:04:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That "I won't lose" feeling can lead to growth
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.10,1:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and become the energy to work hard. I want to be that kind of person too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.62,1:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have those feelings myself sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.36,1:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "I'm so jealous of her," and things like that. Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.88,1:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.96,1:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single day, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.92,1:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.74,1:04:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand, Shizuku...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.96,1:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, towards the girls who were seriously aiming for the center position...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.84,1:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She said some things she shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.04,1:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.58,1:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everyone who knows Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.08,1:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,understands that about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.20,1:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that she had bad intentions.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.72,1:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku was just so overwhelmed at the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.32,1:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and she could only see what was right in front of her. That's why she blurted out that someone else might be better for the center.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.52,1:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It just came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.42,1:04:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that feeling too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.80,1:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure of being the center is insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.44,1:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the expectations and her persona... Shizuku wasn't being her true self.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.62,1:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a character she maintained thanks to everyone, which made it even harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.20,1:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was part of it too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.28,1:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Comment: 0,1:05:15.36,1:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.36,1:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so raw.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.50,1:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.91,1:05:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.08,1:05:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so intense.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.16,1:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At such a sensitive, young age,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.40,1:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and on top of that, having to be chosen by someone else to succeed...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.00,1:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.92,1:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard alone won't make you the center.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.92,1:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You need someone to recognize you and say, "You're the center."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.92,1:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it so tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.08,1:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I suppose that's exactly why they're able to shine so brightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.08,1:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.96,1:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at this scenario, I thought to myself...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.08,1:05:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"I really need to be careful."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.60,1:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of this past, we have the present.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.92,1:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Without this, MORE MORE JUMP! wouldn't have been born, and I'm so grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.75,1:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.80,1:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku said "Thank you" too. Truly, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.34,1:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Arisa-chan also stuck to her guns until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.52,1:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing she said was wrong. Her actions might have been a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.12,1:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but her words weren't wrong at all. Even during the AiHaza recording we just watched,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.76,1:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you might wonder why she'd say such things on a TV show, but she knew the viewers wanted to see idols have those deep conversations, so she did it to liven up the program.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.52,1:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She worked with Marina-chan and the Cheerful*Days members to make it exciting, and you can really feel her dedication.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.38,1:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a true professional.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.66,1:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.40,1:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nerve-wracking, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.96,1:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so anxious, wondering how it would turn out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.44,1:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's not a bad person at heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.08,1:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just very straightforward, serious, and strict with both herself and others.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.48,1:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I really wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.68,1:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up rambling quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.04,1:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.84,1:07:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.00,1:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.20,1:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.24,1:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're working your hardest, your perspective becomes subjective.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.10,1:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only see what's right in front of you. In those moments, you need to pull the camera back like a drone...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.76,1:07:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to look at things from a broader, bird's-eye view.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.60,1:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, even in moments when you're wondering "Why?"...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.52,1:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you might realize the other person had their own position or feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.60,1:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can understand what was happening where you couldn't see, I'm sure you'll be able to reach an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.60,1:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll help you communicate better too. This is a great lesson for daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.44,1:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.18,1:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that was...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.60,1:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the story.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.12,1:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a turning point where Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.88,1:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,took a step forward. We saw her purity, her strength,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.64,1:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and just how cool she can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.87,1:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.92,1:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the title "Beyond the Untangled Threads" includes the word "thread"...
Comment: 0,1:08:44.56,1:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.56,1:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The lyrics of "Metamolibbon" also mention "thread," which is a key word. It's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.76,1:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think these little connections are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.06,1:08:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.56,1:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone has different thoughts, so please tweet them using the hashtag.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.30,1:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very raw story, so the characters people empathize with will probably vary.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.08,1:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to have many different feelings, so I hope you all share those too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.60,1:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.35,1:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was a fascinating scenario.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.25,1:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.75,1:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.24,1:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being quite serious, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.17,1:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.52,1:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I even surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.36,1:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm alone today and the story was so impactful, I came prepared to say what I really wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.60,1:09:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have moments like this too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.94,1:09:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I often serve as the MC for things like the Wondershow Channel, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.16,1:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there was a moment when everyone saw me alone
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.36,1:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and felt a bit uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.52,1:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have times when I speak seriously like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.40,1:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.00,1:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.30,1:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.20,1:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, although it was only for a short while...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.74,1:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This concludes the "Proseka After Talk: Beyond the Untied Thread" edition.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.44,1:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to everyone who watched the stream.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.52,1:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching all the comments you were sending.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.56,1:10:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't get to all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.76,1:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.63,1:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to join the same room for a Virtual Live like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.36,1:10:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and connecting with people watching the stream in real-time has a different kind of appeal
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.16,1:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,than watching alone, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.24,1:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it for all of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.48,1:10:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.70,1:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.20,1:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.20,1:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.44,1:11:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't finished the "Beyond the Untied Thread" story yet, you can read it all in the Event Stories menu once the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.64,1:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, read it as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.78,1:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.72,1:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, thank you very much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.32,1:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
